flowchart LR
    A[Quantized model] --> B[Measure per-block\nreconstruction error]
    B --> C{Error too high?}
    C -->|yes| D[Add low-rank\ncompensation matrix]
    D --> E[W * A_r * B_r\nadded to quantized W]
    C -->|no| F[Keep quantized block]
    E --> G[W4A8 or W8A8\n+ LoRC correction]
    F --> G
